{
  "stem": "4345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after 12 days of suffering in this camp, what I went through, what I saw, again, there was an-- an order given that we must meet tomorrow morning-- after-- this was after 10-- after 12 days, I think.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have to meet in the front on the-- by the tracks, in front of the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got down and there's a cattle wagon-- cattle wagons are waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We already were out-- from the 900 girls maybe 500 were left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, they lost-- we lost the lives there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we were put on those cattle trains for eight days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], if anybody is going to tell you this is impossible that it happened, don't ever let them say it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I lived it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was on it, and I'm here to tell you that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Eight days in a closed cattle wagon without air, food, toilet, water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We laid there like-- like dead animals, but the heart was going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Twice on the eight-day trip, it arrived from plus Flossenburg to Bergen-Belsen, OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They opened the doors and the we had to throw the dead bodies out onto tracks because people died in that-- in the-- in the wagon and the car, and we had to throw them out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one time this Gestapo standing by the door, and he's drinking from the-- you know, water from his-- what do you call this-- this-- the soldiers use?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The canteen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From his canteen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I said to him, [SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can I have a little water?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, danke schoen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he takes and spills it out right in front of me and he closes the door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just an example of humanity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
